casebody.data:
No. 86,

Mise.

Roberts v. Memphis Street Railway Co. *890Grover N. McCormick for petitioner. Roane Waring and Sam P. Walker for respondent. Per Curiam.:

Petition for writ of certiorari granted. The order of the Court of Appeals is vacated and the case is remanded to that court for further consideration in the light of the opinion of this Court in Adkins v. DuPont de Nemours & Co., ante, p. 331.
